sequenceDiagram
    Client->>+UI: Initiates conversation with ChatBot
    UI->>+ChatBot: Receive user's initiation
    ChatBot->>+Controller: Handle user's initiation
    Controller->>ChatBot: Determine user's request type
    ChatBot->>+Controller: User asks for a basic query
    Controller-->>-ChatBot: Query type identified
    ChatBot->>Controller: Fetch and process basic query
    Controller-->>-ChatBot: Provide response
    ChatBot-->>-UI: Send response to UI
    UI-->>-Client: Display ChatBot response

    Client->>+UI: Requests navigation to a specific page
    UI->>+ChatBot: User requests page navigation
    ChatBot->>+Controller: User requests navigation
    Controller-->>ChatBot: Request type identified
    ChatBot->>Controller: Process navigation request
    Controller-->>-ChatBot: Perform page navigation
    ChatBot-->>-UI: Send requested page to UI
    UI-->>-Client: Display requested page
